title: Thousands stranded in Bali as volcanic ash grounds planes
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Thousands stranded in Bali as volcani... Thousands stranded in Bali as volcanic ash grounds planes Next Story Prev Story 2 hrs ago Read more: The Age 
Thousands of people stranded in Bali will be waiting for a decision on Saturday afternoon whether flights out of Denpasar will resume after plumes of dangerous volcanic ash grounded planes. Virgin will announce at 1pm local time whether its afternoon flights will operate and Jetstar has said it will update customers at midday on Saturday.
